_sText:
Who says jail break maps have to be ugly? ever notice how most jail break maps look like total crap? no vis or rad data (view data or Lighting). well not any more! in this brand new map by TopHATTwaffle you can escape from jail in style! this map has 32 cells and HDR lighting to make for a better jail experience. Each cell has a individual open/close, as well as a mass cell open in the room outside the armory (CT Spawn). and after 60 seconds the cell doors will auto open. so dick CTs cant rune the game for you any more!

What got fixed?
Major crash bug on map spawn
Whole underground Lab secret
Soccer field
Eating area
Cells can now be closed
Guns can no longer be spammed
Fixed crash on map spawn with 10+ players
